<br>
Change SBs and NSs to 2.5 specs, make vanish/shadow run/viper available to each realm, give Inf's an extra 50 hps. That will make us equivalent, assuming they stop nerfing LA every patch. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uharanavei.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Haranavei</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/28/02 8:57:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3639.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Please don't give SBs 2.5....</span><hr size=1> &quot;...any assassin can use 2 handers. Staves are 2 handed so get over it. &quot;<br>
<br>
Ok, let me explain the difference between using a stave, or playing Midgard. Say you're a Shadowblade and you full spec Axe. Your damage variance with both a 1 hand AND the 2 hand axe is based upon your skill level in Axe. With full spec, it's pretty damn good. Pick up a sword. With no points in sword, check out your damage cap/variance. Let's see, numbers all over the place? Can't count on it to hit near your cap? No styles? Congratulations! Now you know what it's like to wield a stave.<br>
<br>
