<br>
Celtic Dual: CRAP 99% of all shades only put the last little bit of spec points into it, the styles are absolutely awful and I have a Blademaster who is full spec in it so they don't get any better with points, So SB's you are not the only ones with a crap spec line. I really feel for the BM's since that's supposed to be the main thing for them.<br>
<br>
Will I say that Shades suck? No, we do ok. I think the spells need some love still and that CD needs mucho work but on the lines that do work they work pretty good. As to the &quot;High&quot; evades. All the other assasins get the same evade that I do. <br>
<br>
