<br>
Are Inf's good, yup I fight them all the time. Are they vastly supperior not that I see but I lose and they lose. Would I like to see 2.5? Yeah I would cause if my &quot;strong spellcaster&quot; spells don't get some love I want to get it somewhere else.<br>
<br>
Do I think that Inf's are in the lead as far as assasins go? Yeah, not by a ton but about 450 spec points or so. Should SB's and NS's get the same spec? Yeah, or near to it. My spells don't make a huge difference, not as much as say a 2h weapon does.<br>
<br>
The spec as I see it:<br>
<br>
Infiltrator: 2.5 or +450<br>
Shadowblade: 2.35 or + about 300 or so<br>
Nightshade: 2.35 or +300 or so<br>
<br>
The reason?<br>
<br>
SB's have 2h and xtra hp's<br>
NS's have a shout<br>
<br>
That's how I see it, those extra hp's/2h weapon and shout are worth about 150 points in spec. <p>-Jorahs <BR>
